&lt;p&gt;Calyxo is seeking a highly skilled and innovative electrical engineer to help develop electronic subsystems in kidney stone treatment. This role focuses on the design of PCBAs, cable harnesses, and prototype embedded software for integration of sensing, controls, and communication subsystems into safe and reliable products. This is a hands-on technical leadership role for an engineer who enjoys developing both hardware and embedded software, working across electromechanical, controls systems, and software boundaries to deliver clinically robust performance. This role requires ensuring that all engineering efforts comply with industry standards and regulatory requirements, while aligning with strategic business objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
